{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)unregisterForPushNotifications:","role":"symbol","title":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"Unregisters the device from push notifications.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/unregisterforpushnotifications:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/unregisterForPushNotifications:"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":" (^","kind":"text"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError","text":"NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":")) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when unregistration completes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Receives nil on success or an NSError on failure.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"completion"}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Removes the device from receiving push notifications:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Notifies Pushwoosh servers to stop sending notifications to this device"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes the device token from Pushwoosh"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this when the user logs out, deletes their account, or explicitly disables notifications."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Example","level":2,"text":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregister during user logout:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class AuthenticationManager {","","    func logout(completion: @escaping (Result<Void, Error>) -> Void) {","        \/\/ Show loading indicator","        LoadingIndicator.show()","","        \/\/ First, unregister from push to stop receiving notifications for this user","        Pushwoosh.configure.unregisterForPushNotifications { [weak self] error in","            if let error = error {","                Logger.warning(\"Push unregistration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                \/\/ Continue with logout even if unregistration fails","            }","","            \/\/ Clear user session","            self?.clearUserSession()","","            \/\/ Clear user tags","            Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                \"logged_in\": false,","                \"user_id\": NSNull(),","                \"email\": NSNull()","            ])","","            \/\/ Stop server communication if required by privacy policy","            if UserDefaults.standard.bool(forKey: \"clearDataOnLogout\") {","                Pushwoosh.configure.stopServerCommunication()","            }","","            LoadingIndicator.hide()","            completion(.success(()))","        }","    }","","    private func clearUserSession() {","        KeychainManager.shared.clearCredentials()","        UserDefaults.standard.removePersistentDomain(forName: Bundle.main.bundleIdentifier!)","        CoreDataManager.shared.clearUserData()","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/unregisterForPushNotifications:":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/unregisterForPushNotifications:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/unregisterforpushnotifications:","title":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregisters the device from push notifications."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:"}]}}}